{
  "stem": "8784.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "In this camp, life was much more bearable, and we began to sense-- in a short while, we began to sense that maybe we do have a chance to survive the war in this concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was somehow in the air.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "With Schindler being there and with the SS guards not entering too much of the camp, we began to think that maybe something is changing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Maybe we-- we do have a chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I was taken-- on many days, I was taken out of this concentration camp together with another fellow by the name of Blazenstein, who now lives in Israel-- or the last I heard of lived in Israel.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] The two of us would be marched out of this camp in Brunnlitz and taken to his villa.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The villa was located in a mill, inside a mill behind the water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were separated from the road by a-- by a canal of water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And in that villa, the two of us were supposed to fix-- repair his-- Schindler-- Oskar Schindler's furniture, maintain it cleaned.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I have no idea whether Oskar Schindler ever stayed there or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I don't remember seeing Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Schindler or Oskar Schindler at that villa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "On the other hand, I remember them in the--.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "In the factory itself, there were accommodations where Oskar Schindler stayed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Off the factory hall, there were some rooms that they were living in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "On many occasions, I was able to jump out of the villa window.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the reason I could do that because in those days, in 1945 late into the war, the SS guards were no longer those spic-and-span young devils, the young killers of SS, but they were the older people now serving in the-- in the army and not being on the front.",
      "word_count": 51
    }
  ],
